# Resonance Contract Rule

Use the `resonance-contract` workflow from this repository when the user asks for:

- resonance pairing on `ResonanceContract`
- CA-only user-side participation
- `CreatePairRequestByCa`
- `ConfirmPairRequestByCa`
- `JoinPairQueueByCa`
- `LeavePairQueueByCa`
- pair status lookup, queue status lookup, pending diagnosis, expired diagnosis, already-resonated diagnosis, warmup diagnosis, reward-balance diagnosis, or wrong-call-path / older-route receipt diagnosis for pasted receipts

## Canonical Package

- `skills/resonance-contract/SKILL.md`
- `skills/resonance-contract/references/flows/`
- `skills/resonance-contract/references/examples/`
- `skills/resonance-contract/references/output-contract.md`

Load the canonical package and follow it exactly. Do not duplicate the workflow inside this rule file.
